Generally about .55-.66 or so of a number of attempted attacks will be a hit when you're a melee above 200 skill.  Haven't really parsed it in several levels, but at about 230 1HS, I hit about that, depending on where I'm fighting.  Luclin I miss a good bit, Velious I hit more, PoP I "think" I hit a little more often than Velious, and I smack Kunark and old world stuff all the time.<br />_________________<br />Darlatan Firemist
